This pretty much ends the Flimtsones cartoon series other than a few other minor things. This runs like a Hallmark movie and has the parents interfere in the kids new life in Hollywood, sorry Hollyrock. The original creators Hanna and Barbera make cameos but would die a few years after this ending the original guiding force to The Flintsones series. The live action film would come out after renewing the series. It took over 30 years for Pebbles to grow up and have kids of her own. Seems realistic actually. Unfortunately there are no special features. This TV movie should have been paired with its predecessor where the kids get married.
